                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Solemn thing within the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Soul</l>
                    <l>To feel itself get ripe - </l>
                    <l>And golden hang - while<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 farther up - </l>
                    <l>The Maker's Ladders stop - </l>
                    <l>And in the Orchard far below -</l>
                    <l>You hear a Being - drop - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A wonderful - to feel the sun </l>
                    <l>Still toiling at the cheek </l>
                    <l>You thought was finished - </l>
                    <l>Cool of eye, and critical of<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Work -</l>
                    <l>He shifts the stem - a little - </l>
                    <l>To give your Core - a look - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>But solemnest - to know </l>
                    <l>Your chance in Harvest moves </l>
                    <l>A little nearer - Every sun</l>
                    <l>The single - to some lives.  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
